      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Darth Plagueis was a Dark Lord of the Sith, so powerful and so wise he
    could use the Force to influence the midichlorians to create life\u2026 He had
    such a knowledge of the dark side that he could even keep the ones he cared about
    from dying. The dark side of the Force is a pathway to many abilities some consider
    to be unnatural. He became so powerful\u2026 the only thing he was afraid of
    was losing his power, which eventually, of course, he did. Unfortunately, he
    taught his apprentice everything he knew, then his apprentice killed him in his
    sleep. Ironic. He could save others from death, but not himself.\r\n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
